      "content": "Note that the action availability is based on the current date that the menu item is on.\n- Past: delete and log are not available\n- Present (current date): both delete and log are available\n- Future: only delete is avalable\n\nThe \"View meal detail\" button (the button with the arrow right icon) is always available"
